In the MATTER OF DISCIPLINE OF Keith Allan VANDERBURG No. D-3064 Supreme Court of the United States. February 24, 2020

Keith Allan Vanderburg, of Independence, Ohio, is suspended from the practice *1258of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
